Package algref

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Citable
    This interface declares the methods that return Publication objects and are to be implemented by algorithm classes that should be citable.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Address
    Objects of this class hold the address information.
    Author
    Objects of this class hold the data about the authors of publications and algorithms, where necessary.
    BookChapterPublication
    Objects of this class represent book chapter publications.
    BookPublication
    Objects of this class represent book publications.
    ConferencePublication
    Objects of this class represent conference publications.
    JournalPublication
    Objects of this class represent journal publications.
    Publication
    This class is used for representing the data about a citable research publication.
    PublicationExporter
    This class implements the logic for exporting the publication info to a standard format for inclusion in reports and papers.
    Publisher
    Objects of this class hold the published info.
